title: Bayside "I Will Follow You Into The Dark"
description:
This song was featured on "Bayside/I Am the Avalanche" which was a limited edition EP by I Am the Avalanche that was distributed on tour. Track listing was:

Bayside:

   1. "I Will Follow You Into The Dark" (Death Cab for Cutie Cover)

I Am the Avalanche:

   2. "Drinking Song"
